    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted on the basis that the ASTM F1717 protocol is a standardized, single-configuration test and no alternative configuration exists within the standard. Overall credibility evidence is sufficient for a Medium assurance level determination supporting the 510(k) submission.",
